data.description: This beautifully remodeled home has a huge living room to relax in. Nice size kitchen to prepare all your delicious meals to include new cabinets, island, granite countertops, backsplash, flooring, sink and appliances.  Enjoy many dinners in the dining room. 1st floor powder room with new vanity and toilet. First and second floors have been repainted with new carpet in the bedrooms and office. Upstairs bathroom has new LVT floor, vanity and toilet. Hardwood floors in living and dining room.  1st floor laundry, new entry door in garage and new lighting throughout first and second floor. 3rd floor has a playroom and 4th bedroom. Roomy porch, deck off of bedroom 3 and patio between house and garage. Home also has replacement windows. Check out this move in remodeled home.
